---
title: Creamy Asparagus & Bacon Pasta Bake with Parmesan & Lemon
description: You’re going to prep this creamy dreamy baby in a flash, then let the oven do the rest of the work. Penne pasta bubbles away in a velvety lemon-cream sauce along with crispy bacon, asparagus, onion, and garlic beneath a golden topping of Parmesan. You’ll whip it out of the oven (with mitts of course!), then it’s straight to the table to serve family style for an easy, filling, Alfredo-style crowd-pleaser that will win you all the heart eyes you could ever need!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/659d962b145e14b9dce09051-1a4bdfeb.jpeg
